00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
The user selects the "+" icon
to create a new post.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:09.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
A modal opens where the user
types the content of the message.

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:13.500 line:80% position:20% align:start
After clicking "Submit", the new
post appears at the top of the feed.

00:00:13.500 --> 00:00:18.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
The post includes an "Edit" option
since it is the user's own content.